---
title: Spicy Garlic Bread Bacon Cheeseburgers with Roasted Potato Wedges
description: Tonight, try this easy, but mind-blowing viral burger upgrade—it's the juicy cheddar cheeseburger you love with a crunchy griddled garlic bread bun. The garlic bread's on the outside, so you get all the flavor straight to those lucky tastebuds. Add garlicky roasted potatoes on the side, and a special sauce (psst: ranch + mayo + Sriracha) for dipping and slathering.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/671f96364251e0dbe4bdeaf5-3c7f6a2b.jpeg
